BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:665287@webcampus.unamur.be
SUMMARY:Assignment 1 : DevOps case study analysis doit être rendu
DESCRIPTION:OBJECTIVE\n\nBy group\, you will analyze a case study regarding
	 DevOps factors. You will identify factors that influence the software deli
	very performance of your case study. All your work will be based on the htt
	ps://dora.dev/research/ [1] website.\n\nDELIVERABLE\n\nYou will submit a re
	port that will:\n\n	* Identify key factors in your case study: for each ite
	m of the ”Capabilities” section from the DORA website\, identify the practi
	ces of your case study.\n	* Link factors to DORA metrics: for each factor i
	dentified in the first step\, identify which DORA metric(s) it is connected
	 to and assess whether it enables or does not enable the metric(s). If a fa
	ctor is absent in the case study\, explain how it might impact the DORA met
	rics.\n	* Define a procedure to measure the DORA metrics: Based on the fact
	ors and their impact identified in the previous steps\, define a procedure 
	for measuring each of the four DORA metrics in your case study. Describe th
	e tools that will help you quantify these metrics.\n\nThe links between the
	 factors and the DORA metrics should be as easy to read as possible\, so yo
	u can choose the form it will take to make this possible. Be imaginative!\n
	\nThe evaluation criteria are available in the _Grille d'évaluation_ previe
	w.\n \n\nLinks:\n------\n[1] https://dora.dev/research/\n
	
CLASS:PUBLIC
LAST-MODIFIED:20251104T132157Z
DTSTAMP:20251109T113446Z
DTSTART:20251110T225900Z
DTEND:20251110T225900Z
CATEGORIES:INFOM126
END:VEVENT
